class.name: DiscordUserMessageSummary
class.brief_description: <para>Represents a summary of a DM conversation with a user. </para>

method.name: last_message_id
method.description: <para>Returns the ID of the last message sent in the DM conversation. </para>

method.name: user_id
method.description: <para>Returns the ID of the other user in the DM conversation. </para>
